Ing '''sale''' (''Cymbopogon citratus''), a ausan dang ''lemon grass'' o ''oil grass'' king Ingles ampong ''tanglad'' king Tagalug, metung yang tanaman kareng lugal a mapali o is a ''tropical'' ibat king [[Mauli]]-[[aslagan]]g Asia (''Southeast Asia''). 

==Gamit king pamaglutu==
King [[Filipinas]], gagamitan de ing sale king pamaglutu, lalu na king ''[[lechon]]'' ampong ningnang a manuk.<ref name="tanglad">{{cite web|url=http://www.marketmanila.com/archives/tanglad-lemongrass|title=Tanglad / Lemongrass|date=August 21, 2006|publisher=Market Manila|accessdate=July 27, 2011}}</ref>

